"the device, the attributes that are linked to it will be listed, and a "
"color can be chosen to display each attribute, it is also possible to add"
" a caption for each attribute. In “retrieve records by:“ it will be "
"possible to configure some filters, you can select the type of historical"
" data filter as the “last records”, in “order” (minute, hours, days and "
"months), and you can also choose an interval time, in addition you can "
"still view the records in “Real time”, as new data is received they will "
"be displayed in the chosen view. After everything is configured, a "
"summary will be shown with the chosen name and attributes. When accessing"
" the views, it will be possible to change the size, fix (which will "
"disable the option to change the size) and still delete the views."
